caroons and Open Policy Agent. “It provide a logic language based on Datalog to write authorization policies. It can store data, like JWT, or small conditions like Macaroons, but it is also able to represent more complex rules like role-based access control, delegation, hierarchies.”</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-27T14:55:11.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"kdeldycke/awesome-billing","categoryHTML":"<h2>Contracts</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/steffoz/status/1389946268764475394\">Is this what Enterprise mean?</a> - A use-case of badly designed contract management alienating big enterprise customers. See the <a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=27053246\">associated HN comments</a> on bulk license purchase.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-27T14:54:56.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"kdeldycke/awesome-billing","categoryHTML":"<h2>Invoice</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://ec.europa.eu/cefdigital/wiki/display/CEFDIGITAL/eInvoicing\">EU eInvoicing</a> - European standard on electronic invoice.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-27T14:54:56.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"kdeldycke/awesome-engineering-team-management","categoryHTML":"<h2>Health</h2><h3>Burnout</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://ssir.org/articles/entry/burnout_from_an_organizational_perspective\">Burnout From an Organizational Perspective</a> - “Extensive research by the military on sustainable performance in stressful conditions teaches that leaders should become champions of health, rather than taskmasters.” Describe the symptoms of toxic organizations and how managers can protect their teams from systemic burnout.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-27T14:54:00.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"kdeldycke/awesome-engineering-team-management","categoryHTML":"<h2>Health</h2><h3>Burnout</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.skylyte.io/self-assessment\">What makes you resilient?</a> - A quick test to profile your energy source, the way you deal with stress, and how it impact your team.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-27T14:54:00.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"kdeldycke/awesome-billing","categoryHTML":"<h2>Pricing</h2><h3>Usage-based Pricing</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://webee.technion.ac.il/people/shimkin/PAPERS/Menache-CloudPricing-Conf2011.pdf\">Socially Optimal Pricing of Cloud Computing Resources</a> - “The socially optimal operating point is unique, and can be sustained by a linear, usage-based tariff, which charges a fixed price per unit resource and unit time.” This paper justify usage-based pricing for cloud resources.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-27T14:53:39.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"kdeldycke/awesome-billing","categoryHTML":"<h2>Payments</h2><h3>Bank Accounts</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://bank.codes/swift-code/\">Swift Codes</a> - Swift / BIC codes for personal use only.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-27T14:53:39.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"rockerBOO/awesome-neovim","categoryHTML":"<h2>Plugin</h2><h3>Motion</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/phaazon/hop.nvim\">phaazon/hop.nvim</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/phaazon/hop.nvim\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.7k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1672,\"repo\":\"phaazon/hop.nvim\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Hop is an EasyMotion-like plugin allowing you to jump anywhere in a document with as few keystrokes as possible.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-06-27T14:32:35.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"rockerBOO/awesome-neovim","categoryHTML":"<h2>Plugin</h2><h3>Motion</h3>","itemHTML":